    <PackageReleaseNotes>[General]
- Remove all boilerplate generator out of Utilities and replace it with seperate console program for generator-related task instead. Result in significant file size reduce.
+ Add new module [DataReaderExtension] and [DataTableExtension].
+ Some class model has been renamed.

[SQL]
+ Add ExecuteReader as DataTable.
+ Add extension method [GetSchemaOf&lt;T&gt;] for table schema reader.
+ Add Insert(IEnumerable&lt;T&gt;) overload for DataConnectorExtension

[Data.Enumerable]
+ New methods [ToQueue&lt;T&gt;], [ToStack&lt;T&gt;] and [ToDataTable]

[Data.DataReaderExtension](New Module)
+ New method [GetColumns] which is return column name of given DbDataReader.

[Data.DataTableExtension](New Module)
+ New methods [ToEnumerable] and [ToEnumerable&lt;T&gt;] which are convert DataTable into IEnumerable&lt;dynamic&gt; and IEnumerable&lt;T&gt; respectively.
+ New method GetColumns for DataTable column reader.
</PackageReleaseNotes>
